column1: Querying all.csv for SIN cats with weird parents

SELECT c1 as id,c2 as gender,c3 as name,c4 as ems,c5 as dob,c6 as reg,c7 as sire,c8 as dam FROM all.csv WHERE substr(ems,1,3) in ('SIN') AND ( sire NOT IN (SELECT 102964 UNION SELECT c1 FROM all_SIN.csv ) OR dam NOT IN (SELECT 102965 UNION SELECT c1 FROM all_SIN.csv ) )
